{"tid":630961,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"你話 有冇得拍返套港版挑戰者一號?","createTime":"2018-04-16T05:11:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-16T05:18:25.000Z","uid":42601,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1d5554dfcaa59fa7d3faac3c96004e9822b99b15","tid":630961,"uid":42601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T05:11:56.000Z","msg":"睇挑戰者一號 halliday臨尾果句&rdquo;Thank tou for playing my game&rdquo;整喊我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而尋晚香港電影金像獎 一晚可以爆7個post<br />\n令我覺得 愛香港(電影)既人比想像中多<br />\n<br />\n或者可以拍套戲 先度好情節 係想帶出一d大部分香港人面對既困境<br />\n之後係對白/鏡頭當中放入80-00年代既集體回憶 (e.g. 星爺造型、子華梗、LF2...<br />\n當然要劇情嚴謹紮實為先 唔可以hard sell為加彩蛋而加<br />\n<br />\n如果牽涉政治議題 分分鐘變成下一齣「十年」<br />\n咁呢齣戲就叫「廿年」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後作為土生土長既香港人,我都想講句<br />\nThank you for supporting Hong Kong movies!"},{"pid":"e5a178989e34cf1c145aaf8c1a9a1ef921152eee","tid":630961,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T05:15:40.000Z","msg":"痴撚線"},{"pid":"004c9c9f0d915a51f5dca95bb376c35abf275076","tid":630961,"uid":42601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5a178989e34cf1c145aaf8c1a9a1ef921152eee","tid":630961,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T05:15:40.000Z","msg":"痴撚線"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T05:18:25.000Z","msg":"點痴法?大家坐低 飲啖茶食個包 傾掂佢ok?"}]}